Author: WILSON
Vol / Page: 436
Edition:
Quote: <i>Asplenium</i> SPLEENWORTS ...Both the botanical and the common names refer to the old belief that these ferns were useful medicinally against complaints of the spleen. More than 700 species of the genus occur throughout the world.
